## Financial Due Diligence: Meridian Healthcare
### Quality of Earnings and Cash Flow Assessment

@notes: Key QoE finding: $31M in addbacks are either one-time in name only or non-recurring costs that reflect real operating requirements. The adjusted EBITDA of $117M is the correct acquisition basis.

